data.text:
CountryCode.org is your complete guide to make a call from anywhere in the world, to anywhere in the world. This page details Hungary phone code.

The Hungary country code 36 will allow you to call Hungary from another country. Hungary telephone code 36 is dialed after the IDD. Hungary international dialing 36 is followed by an area code.

The Hungary area code table below shows the various city codes for Hungary. Hungary country codes are followed by these area codes. With the complete Hungary dialing code, you can make your international call.
